title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Musical Instruments & Related Accessories
description: Imports Intra Eu - Musical Instruments & Related Accessories in the United Kingdom increased to 12.03 GBP Million in September from 8.97 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Musical Instruments & Related A in the United Kingdom averaged 6.09 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 17.56 GBP Million in November of 2020 and a record low of 1.03 GBP Million in July of 1996.
